nodes.text: Headhunter Six was the callsign used by one of Jessa Vandangante's mechanics when flying with Headhunter Flight during the Battle of the Outlaw Tech Base, in 2 BBY. He was a member of the Vandangante outlaw techs, and having no prior combat experience was the third and final casualty in the squadron. He was the brother of Headhunter Five.
